column2: SELECT p.objId,p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.expAB_r,     p.dered_u as u, p.dered_g as g, p.dered_r as r, p.dered_i as i,      s.z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM galaxy AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE      (s.BOSS_TARGET1 & dbo.fBossTarget1(&&&) > # or (s.primTarget & dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) > #))     and s.z > #     and s.z < #     and s.ra > #     and s.ra < #
